[
    {
        "source_sentence": "維摩詰所說經卷八",
        "translation": "Vimalakīrti-nirdeśa-sūtra, Vol. 8",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b09_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛道品",
        "translation": "Chapter on the Buddha-Path",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b10_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時文殊師利。",
        "translation": "It was then that Mañjuśrī asked Vimalakīrti.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b11_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "問維摩詰言。",
        "translation": "Mañjuśrī asked Vimalakīrti.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b11_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩云何通達佛道。",
        "translation": "\"How does a bodhisattva penetrate the Buddha Way?",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b11_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "維摩詰言。",
        "translation": "Vimalakīrti said.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b12_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩行於非道(起照後)。",
        "translation": "\"If a bodhisattva practices what's not the path (after he arouses illumination).",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b12_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是為通達佛道。",
        "translation": "This is called penetrating the Buddha Way.'",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b12_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又問云何菩薩行於非道。",
        "translation": "Again, he asked, \"How does a bodhisattva practice a path that's not the path?",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b13_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "答曰若菩薩行五無間(五逆罪也)。",
        "translation": "He answered, \"Suppose a bodhisattva practices the five heinous sins.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b13_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而無惱恚。",
        "translation": "They don't have anger or distress.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b14_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至於地獄。",
        "translation": "As for hell, there's no pollution from sins (hell is also the fifth heinous crime).",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b14_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無諸罪垢(地獄因)。",
        "translation": "There's no pollution from sins (the cause of hell).",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b14_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至于畜生。",
        "translation": "As for animals, there's no ignorance, conceit, or other faults.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b14_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有無明憍慢等過。",
        "translation": "There's no ignorance, conceit, or other faults.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b14_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至于餓鬼。",
        "translation": "As for hungry ghosts, they're replete with virtue.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b15_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而具足功德。",
        "translation": "They're fully endowed with virtue.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b15_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行色無色界道。",
        "translation": "They practice the path of the form and formless realms.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b15_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不以為勝。",
        "translation": "They don't regard it as superior.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b16_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示行貪欲。",
        "translation": "He demonstrates the practice of desire.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b16_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "離諸染著。",
        "translation": "They're free of defiled attachment.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b16_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示行瞋恚。",
        "translation": "He demonstrates the practice of anger.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b16_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於諸眾生無有恚礙。",
        "translation": "They have no anger toward sentient beings and are not obstructed by anger.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b17_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示行愚癡。",
        "translation": "He demonstrates the practice of folly.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b17_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而以智慧調伏其心。",
        "translation": "He tempered their minds with wisdom.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b17_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示行慳貪。",
        "translation": "He demonstrates the practice of stinginess and greediness.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b18_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而捨內外所有不惜身命。",
        "translation": "He disregards what's inside and outside him and doesn't spare his own life.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b18_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示行毀禁。",
        "translation": "He shows them to practice disregard for the prohibitions.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b19_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而安住淨戒。",
        "translation": "He'll abide in pure morality.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b19_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至小罪。",
        "translation": "It's even a minor offense.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b19_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶懷大懼。",
        "translation": "He still harbors great fear.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b19_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示行瞋恚。",
        "translation": "They show that they're acting angrily.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b19_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而常慈忍。",
        "translation": "He always tolerates kindness.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b20_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示行懈怠。",
        "translation": "He demonstrates laziness in his ways.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b20_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而勤修功德。",
        "translation": "He diligently cultivates virtue.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b20_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示行亂意。",
        "translation": "He shows us practicing distraction ...",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b20_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而常念定。",
        "translation": "He's always mindful of concentration.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b21_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示行愚癡。",
        "translation": "He shows himself practicing foolishness ...",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b21_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而通達世間出世間慧。",
        "translation": "He shows his practice of foolishness and comprehends worldly and transmundane wisdom.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b21_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示行諂偽。",
        "translation": "He demonstrates his practice of deceit ...",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b22_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而善方便隨諸經義。",
        "translation": "He skillfully follows the teachings of the sūtras.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b22_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示行憍慢。",
        "translation": "He demonstrates pride in his ways and conducts himself with pride.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b22_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而於眾生猶如橋梁。",
        "translation": "He's like a bridge over sentient beings.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b22_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示行諸煩惱。",
        "translation": "He demonstrates the practice of afflictions.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b23_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而心常清淨。",
        "translation": "He's always pure in mind.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b23_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示入於魔。",
        "translation": "He shows them how to enter Māra.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b23_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而順佛智慧不隨他教。",
        "translation": "He conforms to the Buddha's wisdom and doesn't follow other teachings.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b24_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示入聲聞。",
        "translation": "He shows them how to enter the śrāvaka community.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b24_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而為眾生說未聞法。",
        "translation": "He teaches the unheard Dharma for sentient beings.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565b24_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示入辟支佛。",
        "translation": "He shows entry to the pratyekabuddhas and accomplishes great compassion.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c01_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而成就大悲。",
        "translation": "They then accomplished great compassion.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c01_23",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "教化眾生。",
        "translation": "He teaches and transforms sentient beings.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c01_24",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示入貧窮。",
        "translation": "He shows them how to enter into poverty.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c02_25",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而有寶手。",
        "translation": "They then had precious hands.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c02_26",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "功德無盡。",
        "translation": "Their merits are inexhaustible.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c02_27",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示入形殘。",
        "translation": "He shows them that he's entered into physical disability.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c02_28",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而具諸好相以自莊嚴。",
        "translation": "He adorns himself with beautiful features.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c03_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示入下賤。",
        "translation": "He's shown entering into lowliness ...",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c03_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而生佛種性中。",
        "translation": "He'll be born within the buddha's seed nature.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c03_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具諸功德。",
        "translation": "They're endowed with merits.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c04_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示入羸劣醜陋。",
        "translation": "He shows us how to enter into a weak and ugly state.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c04_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而得那羅延身。",
        "translation": "He then attains the body of Narayan.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c04_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切眾生之所樂見。",
        "translation": "It's a pleasant sight for all sentient beings.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c04_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示入老病。",
        "translation": "He'll be shown entering old age and illness.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c05_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而永斷病根。",
        "translation": "He'll permanently end the root of illness.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c05_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "超越死畏。",
        "translation": "He transcends the fear of death.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c05_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示有資生。",
        "translation": "He shows that there are necessities for birth.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c06_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而恒觀無常。",
        "translation": "He'll always observe impermanence.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c06_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "實無所貪。",
        "translation": "There's really nothing to desire.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c06_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示有妻妾綵女。",
        "translation": "He shows that there are wives, concubines, and courtesans.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c06_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而常遠離五欲淤泥。",
        "translation": "He's always free of the muck of the five desires.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c07_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "現於訥鈍。",
        "translation": "He shows himself to be dull and inactive.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c07_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而成就辯才。",
        "translation": "They've accomplished eloquence.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c07_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "總持無失。",
        "translation": "His mastery is unimpaired.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c08_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示入邪濟。",
        "translation": "He shows them how to enter into wrong relief.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c08_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而以正濟度諸眾生。",
        "translation": "He uses right relief to save all sentient beings.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c08_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "現遍入諸道。",
        "translation": "He now enters all paths universally.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c09_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而斷其因緣。",
        "translation": "And he ends their causes and conditions.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c09_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "現於涅槃。",
        "translation": "He's now in nirvāṇa.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c09_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而不斷生死。",
        "translation": "And he doesn't stop birth-and-death.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c09_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "文殊師利。",
        "translation": "Mañjuśrī.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c10_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩能如是行於非道(收應前)。",
        "translation": "\"A bodhisattva can thus practice what's not the path (before accepting and responding to it).",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c10_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是為通達佛道。",
        "translation": "This is to fully understand the Buddha Way.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c10_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於是維摩詰。",
        "translation": "It was then that Vimalakīrti asked Mañjuśrī.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c11_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "問文殊師利。",
        "translation": "Mañjuśrī was asked.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c11_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為如來種。",
        "translation": "\"What's the Tathāgata lineage?",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c11_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "文殊師利言。",
        "translation": "Mañjuśrī said.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c12_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有身為種。",
        "translation": "\"The seed of having a body is the seed of the Tathāgata.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c12_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無明有愛為種。",
        "translation": "'Nescience and craving are seeds.'",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c12_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "貪恚癡為種。",
        "translation": "Craving, ill-will, and delusion are seeds.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0565c12_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四顛倒為種。",
        "translation": "Four kinds of delusion are seeds ...",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0566a01_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五蓋為種。",
        "translation": "five hindrances are seeds ...",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0566a01_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六入為種。",
        "translation": "six sense-fields as seeds ...",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0566a01_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七識處為種。",
        "translation": "seven bases of consciousness as seeds ...",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0566a01_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八邪法為種。",
        "translation": "8 wrong dharmas as seeds ...",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0566a02_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九惱處為種。",
        "translation": "nine fields of affliction as seeds ...",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0566a02_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十不善道為種。",
        "translation": "10 unwholesome paths are seeds.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0566a02_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以要言之。",
        "translation": "To summarize, these are the sixty-two views.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0566a03_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六十二見。",
        "translation": "The sixty-two views ...",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0566a03_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及一切煩惱皆是佛種。",
        "translation": "and all afflictions are seeds of a buddha.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0566a03_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "曰何謂也。",
        "translation": "What do you mean by that?",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0566a03_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "答曰。",
        "translation": "He answered.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0566a04_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若見無為入正位者。",
        "translation": "'If someone sees nothingness and enters the correct stage, then they can't again give rise to the mind of unsurpassed, correct enlightenment.'",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0566a04_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不能復發阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心。",
        "translation": "They can't again give rise to the mind of unsurpassed, correct enlightenment.",
        "source": "X19n0347_008:0566a04_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
